{"tid":1266550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會展提早關閉　有展覽參展商指大失預算　","createTime":"2019-06-29T14:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T16:30:31.000Z","uid":20933,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1e4b860a646331e85f69029b366b5617145ba1","tid":1266550,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"政府基於安全及保安理由，決定明天將會展全面關閉，原訂明日結束的家居博覽和寵物展，要提前今晚結束。<br />\n<br />\n兩個展覽的主辦機構發言人表示，是在下午才接獲會展通知，對決定感到非常無奈，指影響十分大，包括要取消明天的活動及抽起宣傳，原本預料明天是入場人數高峰，提前結束令參展商損失慘重，門票收益損失預料達整體的4成。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又認為展覽不涉政治，指政府不應在未有公眾示威前就決定關閉會展，影響展覽，會再與會展商討賠償安排。<br />\n<br />\n不少參展商晚上都貼出減價告示。有參展商不滿政府未有解釋，就作出決定，影響展覽，令他大失預算。他指今日要清走貨物，在人手和運輸上安排困難，估計損失達幾十萬，要減價「益街坊」散貨，相當無奈。"},{"pid":"997699f0f87f7b6ea526db275fc96c5b64f95378","tid":1266550,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:39:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1127711&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1127711%26csid%3D261_341&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=7b1eb22a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1127711&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"5f7011b838d2e0d306acb88029a21efcbd22f7ca","tid":1266550,"uid":114801,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:40:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府"},{"pid":"fdab6aa44dcaa88c78ac91fdfc52a3e4107ffd5f","tid":1266550,"uid":36238,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:41:03.000Z","msg":"張建宗仆街到 搞到民不聊生 升少日旗洗唔洗死?"},{"pid":"07210db21a5e6e9822349f195be8279727694616","tid":1266550,"uid":3775,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"又係全港買單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a14bcf9d4bec0c7cb0f3ea2daafa298aea74dac","tid":1266550,"uid":531,"like":4,"dislike":0,"sc